cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) tasks such as named entity recognition (NER) and word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related tasks. The paper also involves machine learning models, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of word embeddings could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
